- Fresh databases apply both active migrations with `npx prisma migrate deploy`
- Never manually edit migration SQL files
- Historical SQL is immutable under `prisma/migration_archive/pre_v2_consolidation`
- Follow `prisma/MIGRATION_BASELINE_RUNBOOK.md`; production operations require explicit approval
- Lock file ensures consistent provider across environments
